黔首詞解以資詞解敵國，卻賓客以業詞解諸侯，使天下之士退而不敢西向，裹足不入秦，此所謂「藉寇兵而齎盜糧 詞解」者也</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:04:55.000Z","msg":"人無異國，只有中國<br />\n普天之下，莫非王土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9d698789ff835ca0d978f7cb78a6b437554d99","tid":1901651,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"左膠總統唔係送左300萬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0859311e21ef7df8eb7ff1258ab18f8485d30a7a","tid":1901651,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bb3205316f23dac7f4eda97590ef31b93e9c8b6","tid":1901651,"uid":184679,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/f360da2e-502b-4201-96e9-511d9aa2b1c0_tv_w1200_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2Ff360da2e-502b-4201-96e9-511d9aa2b1c0_tv_w1200_r1_s.jpg&h=2a49ae40&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86cf162fe252470effce6b88710aa56b67c235e","tid":1901651,"uid":20713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"屌你2.5萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379bd2c00b7ebd6c7ec5cc53fa0d87dfbcf5748a","tid":1901651,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"南韓武漢肺炎又有新源頭一一國產口罩。"},{"pid":"332f449a7bdb16b4f7445e1124d20aa12986a4f1","tid":1901651,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"批貨可能係之前支那係韓國搶番黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":